  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Build Accessible Toilets for pupils with disablity</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Due to poor hygiene conditions characterized by dirty and inaccessible toilets in local schools leading to school drop out and infectious diseases among pupils with disabilities . This project will provide accessible toilets and access to clean and safe water in 15 schools. This will improve on the hygiene conditions of 500 pupils on wheelchairs and the blind who crawl and touch in filthy material in order to reach the toilet openings. &quot;A disease free environment  accelerates quality education&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
